Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:19.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:25.05,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:30.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:36.95,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:42.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:48.69,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:52.82,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:57.94,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:01:01.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:06.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:12.38,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:18.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:24.14,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.21,0:01:37.91,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,169)}RAINY NIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:49.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't have to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I go and say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:58.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"And here I thought you were a squadron commander."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"All right, fine! You want me to go, I'll go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"And hurry."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Understood."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'm sorry. It's been so long since\Nwe've seen each other."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am an awful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now now, why the harsh look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. Something happened\Nbetween you two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:26.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. You can lie, but it's\Nwritten all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Things aren't going too well\Nwith the boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:30.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:34.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my hands on something nice that\NI thought I'd give to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? It's top-grade black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? This is so rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've secured plenty for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I picked a good time\Nto give it to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you and the boy are fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,you two can drink that together\Nand make up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always best to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:17.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.\NGo ahead and take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put her in the hangar for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase wanted me to\Ntell you to contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:32.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She just wants me to hand in\Nmy patrol report, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I need her to tell me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I can't stand people who get\Ntoo wrapped up in their work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All quiet again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My report, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:00.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:03.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that stunt you pulled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you said that out of jealousy,\Nit was pretty low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealousy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "if," didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:13.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that would never happen with you.\NIt was just out of enthusiasm for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:16.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that's important\Nto you is your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mad, aren't you? I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got to see her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have at least given me\Nsome time to talk to Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not very feminine, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:31.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be stifling having to work under\Nsomeone like her every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go out for some tea sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,M-me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is inappropriate.\NI'm on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's all right to play hooky\Nevery once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you should be saying\Nthings like that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase is in love with you, isn't she, Captain Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa? In love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:59.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! The only thing she\Nlives for is her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And here I was trying\Nto apologize to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo sure is dense, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he just doesn't understand\Na woman's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from what just went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say the Major still hasn't come clean\Nwith him about how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:23.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is frustrating, watching from the sidelines.\NYou have to proclaim your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping it all locked up inside\Nis so old-fashioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Major's just not very open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's jealous, she should\Ncome right out and say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe her heart's just not\Nwired the same as ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd tell him "I love you!"\NIn front of everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have an severe\Ncase of exhibitionism!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad when men are dense, but it's really\Nbad when they're too sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:57.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always eavesdropping on\Ngirl talk, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rip your pants off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He thinks I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:04.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I say there's something wrong with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It's always best to be honest."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:21.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, even I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The only thing that's important\Nto you is your job."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You're not very feminine, are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something did happen, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:05.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel like having that\Ntea with the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,why not drink it over at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain won't be letting up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something stronger,\NI'd rather have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do drink sometimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is wine okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really so terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:07.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did the boy say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:13.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I was going to use that tea you\Ngave me to try to apologize to him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I really am not very feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:23.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,People are people. And having different\Nkinds of people is a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am trying to open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But every time I'm in front of Hikaru, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not drunk yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's saying you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how things are between you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,just be thankful that the man\Nyou love is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After he died, this is what got\Nme through the nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that now though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:00.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Were things always good between\Nyou and Major Focker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After we ran into each other again\Non the Macross, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But before then, it was all fits and starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you like me to tell\Nyou about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This I've got to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:30.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I did go a little too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him back during the Unification Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:40.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I enlisted, I was stationed at\Na base in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was so naive back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's where he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hey, baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Look over here! Over here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hey, cutie!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:03.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Lieutenant! New recruits!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:09.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'm Lt. Roy Focker! At your service, ladies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:11.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hi there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't until a week later\Nthat I spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"There they are!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"These guys coming in from the front\Nare the only ones you picked up?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.17,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roger. It's just the five planes coming in\Nfrom the southwest."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:48.07,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Your name's Claudia, isn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.18,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're pretty cute!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lt. Focker?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"How about a date sometime?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:57.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even out here in the boonies they've\Ngot some pretty good restaurants."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"When's good for you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.36,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lieutenant! Please refrain from\Npersonal conversations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.69,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you really think this is the right time?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.09,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's improper!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.40,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh yeah, I like that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:11.23,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's exactly the prim\Nway new recruits should be!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:47.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, my first impression\Nof him wasn't a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:54.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I didn't really\Nunderstand how his mind worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:01.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, half out of curiosity, I agreed to a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:20.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey! Sorry I'm late."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:28.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I totally forgot I had a date\Nwith my friends here."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.87,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You don't mind if they come along, do you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.47,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, squeeze together a little!\NSomeone else is getting in."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.41,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Come on, hop in! What's the matter?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's all right. Excuse me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.95,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}"Hey, wait!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.01,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Forget about her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hurry up, let's go for a drive!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I went home in shock, wondering if he was\Nbold or just incredibly thoughtless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.44,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm on duty. This is inappropriate."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:14.39,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to come here every day\Nuntil you go on a date with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.54,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You can't be serious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.79,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Enemy fighters closing in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.19,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, no!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.02,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"'Til tomorrow, then."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.85,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Claudia, patch me through to the main base."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.78,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Claudia!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:44.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea. I can't believe the Major\Nhad a side like that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:48.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, he was operating way outside\Nthe bounds of what made sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:54.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I missed him when he wasn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like my heart was being twisted in knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he sent to the front lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:03.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Unification Wars ended and he was\Ntransferred to South Ataria Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:10.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, but he never wrote me a single\Nletter, not for a whole year,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and after he'd made a spectacle of himself\Ncoming to see me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you came to the Macross too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Being transferred to the same base as him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:28.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to school for full-time crew training where\NI met you and we became roommates...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to understand the ties that\Nbind people together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And their hearts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long I waited,\Nhe never came to say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,so I made up my mind to go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.42,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's been a long time."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, hi! It's you. How are you?\NI heard you'd come here."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.54,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, I'd like to give you these back."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:07.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"What are these? Oh... you kept this stuff?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.05,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ah, that is, if you insist."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:14.55,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Feast your eyes on this baby!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:18.55,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's still under development, but it's a new kind of\Nfighter that will even be able to transform,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"the VF-X-1."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:24.51,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Its speed and engine performance blow away\Nanything that's ever been flown."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:29.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"We're finally taking her up for\Na test flight tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.06,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Huh? Hey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:32.78,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right after that, I fell into a\Nbad bout of self-loathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:47.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked myself why I didn't just\Ntell him how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:56.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's hard to understand people's hearts\Nbut back then, I really didn't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about two hours or so before\Nthe prototype's test flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't seen him around so I got worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:07.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that he must be holed up\Nby himself somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:11.02,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"No way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.72,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"No!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, how's that? Pretty good, huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:23.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:27.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I felt when I saw him fooling\Naround with those girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:44.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the whole time, I'd been jealous because\NI was only seeing one side of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the night after the test flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it was raining, just like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.30,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hello?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.67,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's me, Focker."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:32.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.18,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to see you, right away."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.94,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you have any idea what time it is?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.33,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}"The middle of the night, probably."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.83,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're drunk, aren't you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.83,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to see you. It will only take a minute."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"This really isn't..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:46.10,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not trying to barge into your room or anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.39,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.77,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"A phone booth across from your quarters."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:50.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're here?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:53.29,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've had a lot to drink, but\NI'm still sober."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:54.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hold on."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:10.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey. I'm sorry to call you out in the\Nmiddle of the night like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.34,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.81,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, I didn't bring a handkerchief with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, that's okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.68,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Did something happen?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.34,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"No..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"No, let me explain."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:30.69,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"This probably won't matter to you at all,\Nbut I want you to hear this."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:34.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Before the prototype test flight today,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.60,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was making an ass of myself with\Nsome of the women in the squad."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:40.38,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"My superiors gave me a good\Nchewing out for it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.54,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"But the thing is, even I get scared."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.85,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's how it is with pilots."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.09,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"People may think that we get into\Nour planes without a care,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:27.68,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"but sometimes we think to ourselves,\N'Am I going to die tomorrow?'"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.73,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"And there are times we can't go through with it\Nunless we say some pretty stupid things."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You mind if I keep going?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.78,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Back when we were at the old base together,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:40.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"it was those feelings that made me\Ngo to your place with bouquets."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:42.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't be mad."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:47.84,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"As you know, I've got lots of women friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:52.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"But you were the only one I thought of when\NI wanted to tell someone about this."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.08,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Today was a low-level flight,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:02.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"but tomorrow, we'll push it to full speed\Nat an altitude of 1,000 meters."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.76,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.09,0:20:08.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's all. Thanks."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:32.04,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Major Hayase is in love with you, isn't she, Captain Ichijo?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's in love with me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. Maybe she's on the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She went home? Two hours ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Hard to believe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:24.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I only knew one side\Nof Major Focker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:27.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with him for real after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:30.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, whatever happens,\Ndon't let it get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:36.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Focker used to tell me about the boy all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's pretty bad at expressing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we both fell for pilots, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:47.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:54.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:01.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to have a drink with this guy tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:07.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but would you mind heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:08.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening! It's Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, beat it! Beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for you to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:27.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always best to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such a weird face.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:53.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I went a little overboard this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:57.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I smell of alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:58.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:00.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a little wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:02.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:08.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I managed to get my hands\Non some pretty rare tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to have some with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:14.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you up on that.\NOkay, let's go to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:17.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'm out of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:20.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. All we need is hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:22.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's something I got plenty of!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:34.18,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(82,106)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:34.18,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,458)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:42.63,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in two years, Hikaru and\NMinmay get to spend time alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.77,0:23:47.77,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this happens only because Hikaru\Nbreaks a picnic date with Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.31,0:23:52.51,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Unaware of this, Misa continues\Nto wait for Hikaru alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:56.88,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"PRIVATE TIME"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:02.05,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,139)}PRIVATE TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.81,0:24:22.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:29.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.47,0:24:35.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:43.54,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.69,0:24:50.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.37,0:24:55.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.27,0:25:03.51,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.87,0:25:14.66,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
